      "title": "Mississauga named Ontario’s Most Active Community in 2026 ParticipACTION Community Challenge",
      "summary": "The City of Mississauga has been named Ontario's Most Active Community in the 2026 ParticipACTION Community Challenge presented by Novo Nordisk. As part of the recognition, the City will receive $5,000 to support physical activity and sport initiatives in the community. This recognition reflects the City’s commitment to promoting active healthy living for residents of all ages and abilities. ParticipACTION is a national initiative that encourages people and communities across Canada to be active through recreation, sport and everyday movement.",
      "url": "https://www.mississauga.ca/city-of-mississauga-news/news/mississauga-named-ontarios-most-active-community-in-2026-participaction-community-challenge/",
      "source": "City of Mississauga",
      "sourceUrl": "https://www.mississauga.ca/city-of-mississauga-news/",
